<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>접근 권한 없음</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 72px;
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .error-message {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .back-link:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-code">403</div>
        <div class="error-message">접근 권한이 없습니다.</div>
        <p>죄송합니다. 이 페이지에 접근할 수 있는 권한이 없습니다.</p>
        <a href="/" class="back-link">홈으로 돌아가기</a>
    </div>
    
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>